#### 41.1.49 Throttle и debounce (Утилиты)

Контроль частоты вызовов.

```js
function debounce(fn, ms) {
  let t;
  return (...args) => {
    clearTimeout(t);
    t = setTimeout(() => fn(...args), ms);
  };
}

function throttle(fn, ms) {
  let last = 0;
  return (...args) => {
    const now = Date.now();
    if (now - last >= ms) { last = now; fn(...args); }
  };
}

input.addEventListener('input', debounce(search, 300));
window.addEventListener('scroll', throttle(updateScrollPos, 100));
```

